│                          │ expressive motif without changing the total parameter count. Specifically, the ring now   │
│                          │ uses CRY gates with a shared parameter cry_ring around the outer ring, and the hub gates  │
│                          │ use CRX gates with a shared parameter crx_hub_edge from the center to edge qubits. This   │
